6. a6( { The main move. The alternative is to take on  d4  immediately, }6...cxd4 7.exd4 Be7 8.Nc3 O-O 9.Qe2 { when White's play is the same, to bring the rook to  d1  and then either play for the  d5 -push or implement attacking ideas like  Qe5 - g5  or later  Rd3 - g3 ( h3 ) or in case of ... b5 - b4 ,  Na4  play on the queenside using the  c5 -square. } )
