4. Nf3( { White develops the knight now. It's important to play this move and not }4.c3 { which allows }4...d5!?  )
4. Nbd7( { This is a conceptually different plan, more in line with the Hanham variation in the Philidor Defence (arising after   }1.e4 e5 2.Nf3 d6 3.d4 Nf6 4.Nc3 Nbd7 { ) }{ . } )
