7. c6{ Black develops in Hanham style - the queen goes to  c7 , the rook on  e8  and then he will make a choice - whether to send the knight to  f8  and  g6 , or the bishop to  f8  and  g7  (after playing ... g6  first) and perhaps then play ... Nf8 - e6 . }
