9. Ne2{ White wants to push  c4 . }
9. c5{ This is Black's best. }
10. b3( { Stopping  ...c4  and preparing  a4  or  c4 . Thrusting immediately with }10.c4 { is also possible, though after }10...dxc4 11.Bxc4 Nd6 12.b3 b6 { Black has good play. } )
