1. e6( { With this choice Black signals that he doesn't mind a transposition to the French after }2.e4 { . } )
2. c4( { In view of our repertoire choices, this is the only move that doesn't allow Black to move-order us. For example }2.Nf3 { allows }2...f5 { and we've been tricked into a Classical Dutch, or }2...Nf6 { and after }3.c4 { we have played   }3.Nf3 { instead of the preferred }3.Bf4 { . } )
